P1 FIX REQUIRED — ObservationGuide.tsx CTA href wrong. Both CTAs link to /record but should link to /practice (the M12 micro-practice stepper). Fix both:

  Line ~31 (null-state CTA): href={`/library/${clipId}/record`} → href={`/library/${clipId}/practice`}
  Line ~86 (main CTA): href={`/library/${clipId}/record`} → href={`/library/${clipId}/practice`}

Without this fix, the Observation Guide bypasses the M12 stepper entirely. Tester sign-off on M11 is on hold until confirmed.
